				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Argach not saying everyone should be able to do everything, but that everyone should be good for more than one thing.  And if a class needs more utility the best option is generally to give it the utility had by the fewest classes.
<br />

<br />
Even wizards, the class who have the greatest DPS in the game have some utility with root and evac.  Closest a warrior comes to that is being able to tank multiple mobs at once.  But since doing that requires AoE taunt, not only can you not be sure every warrior can do it, but it can also only be done every so often.  Warriors even being the best mitigators, practically zero utility.
